nodes.text: This aqua droid was part of a detachment of droids under command of Asajj Ventress and took part in the Battle of Kamino.

During the invasion of Kamino by the Separatists, this aqua droid was part of a detachment of droids tasked with reassembleing assault craft for the attack on Kamino's capital, Tipoca City, which would be dropped into the sea disguised as starship debris from a diversionary space attack. Meanwhile, Obi-Wan Kenobi, who was in Tipoca City during the battle, was curious about the debris falling from the starships as he considered the space attack to be weak, and dived underwater in a Kamino submarine where he discovered the Separatist's plan. This droid was the first to notice Obi-Wan and alerted the other droids who then attacked his submarine.
This Aqua droid only appeared in the episode ARC Troopers and was voiced by Dee Bradley Baker.
